1
00:01:28,940 --> 00:01:35,660
Winter Begonia

2
00:01:35,660 --> 00:01:38,060
Episode 22

3
00:01:38,270 --> 00:01:39,080
Mr. Shang.

4
00:01:39,450 --> 00:01:40,400
-I beg you.
-Stand up.

5
00:01:40,590 --> 00:01:42,120
Help me. Please help me.

6
00:01:42,120 --> 00:01:42,800
Stand up.

7
00:01:43,830 --> 00:01:45,800
Mr. Shang, please save me out of there.

8
00:01:46,160 --> 00:01:47,360
I can earn money for you.

9
00:01:48,630 --> 00:01:50,680
Mr. Shang, only with you,

10
00:01:50,950 --> 00:01:52,310
can I keep singing opera.

11
00:01:52,759 --> 00:01:54,720
With me?

12
00:01:54,830 --> 00:01:56,720
You’ll never sing.

13
00:01:57,229 --> 00:01:59,440
You have no backbone.

14
00:01:59,440 --> 00:02:01,680
How can you be a star on the stage?

15
00:02:02,680 --> 00:02:03,590
Stand up.

16
00:02:06,440 --> 00:02:07,910
If you will,

17
00:02:08,389 --> 00:02:10,720
come to me when you have a chance.

18
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:12,160
I’ll teach you opera.

19
00:02:14,720 --> 00:02:15,080
Mr. Shang.

20
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:15,800
Stand up.

21
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:17,079
How come you kneel again?

22
00:02:17,079 --> 00:02:18,750
Mr. Shang, we need to go now.

23
00:02:18,750 --> 00:02:20,160
If Sixi’er sees it,

24
00:02:20,160 --> 00:02:21,520
he’ll be angry

25
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:22,440
-and make a scene.
-Don’t worry.

26
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:24,440
I’ll take care of this.

27
00:02:25,030 --> 00:02:27,079
I can’t see such a good performer

28
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:28,550
suffer in Yunxi Theater.

29
00:02:29,470 --> 00:02:30,030
Go back.

30
00:02:30,520 --> 00:02:31,470
OK. Go.

31
00:02:31,470 --> 00:02:33,079
Go to wash your clothes.

32
00:02:46,550 --> 00:02:48,520
Mr. Cheng. Are you serious?

33
00:02:50,270 --> 00:02:51,630
You are picky about the performers.

34
00:02:51,750 --> 00:02:53,240
It’s not easy that you like someone.

35
00:02:53,630 --> 00:02:55,270
I will save him out.

36
00:02:56,110 --> 00:02:58,079
But look at what Sixi’er did.

37
00:02:58,600 --> 00:03:00,880
He doesn’t want Zhouzi to be a star.

38
00:03:01,360 --> 00:03:02,360
And he’s always against me.

39
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:03,720
He won’t let him go easily.

40
00:03:04,720 --> 00:03:06,440
We need a further consideration.

41
00:03:07,160 --> 00:03:08,600
Mr. Cheng. Mr. Shang.

42
00:03:08,600 --> 00:03:10,320
I’ll go if you don’t have anything else.

43
00:03:17,550 --> 00:03:19,360
Keep what happened today as a secret.

44
00:03:20,960 --> 00:03:23,360
I don’t want to hear rumors.

45
00:03:23,550 --> 00:03:24,880
Don’t worry, Mr. Cheng.

46
00:03:24,880 --> 00:03:27,360
I am a good secret keeper.

47
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:53,800
Chief, take care.

48
00:03:58,550 --> 00:03:59,550
Chief.

49
00:04:04,750 --> 00:04:07,390
Dezi. Dezi. Dezi.

50
00:04:07,470 --> 00:04:10,670
Chief. Go now.

51
00:04:11,470 --> 00:04:14,470
These are not common soldiers.

52
00:04:14,470 --> 00:04:17,350
Everything will be fine as long as you are alive.

53
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:20,160
Also, you are not alone now.

54
00:04:20,829 --> 00:04:21,829
Go!

55
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:24,550
-Dezi! Dezi! Dezi!
-Dezi!

56
00:04:32,830 --> 00:04:35,159
Guys, put on the civilians’ clothes.

57
00:04:35,670 --> 00:04:37,200
Let’s run to the mountain.

58
00:04:37,200 --> 00:04:37,880
Chief.

59
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:39,600
What about our bros who were caught?

60
00:04:39,880 --> 00:04:41,000
Let’s go out first.

61
00:04:41,320 --> 00:04:43,830
I’ll take care of other things.

62
00:05:05,220 --> 00:05:07,380
(General Headquarters)

63
00:05:34,390 --> 00:05:35,320
Sir,

64
00:05:35,510 --> 00:05:37,230
an independent battalion with 200 soldiers from Nanking

65
00:05:37,550 --> 00:05:39,270
came Peking to inspect the economy and security.

66
00:05:44,110 --> 00:05:45,350
Economy is economy.

67
00:05:45,880 --> 00:05:47,000
Security is security.

68
00:05:47,550 --> 00:05:49,159
A team of 200 people can fight a battle.

69
00:05:50,640 --> 00:05:51,880
Who is their commander?

70
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:53,480
Liu Hanyun.

71
00:05:54,550 --> 00:05:55,670
Is it him?

72
00:05:55,760 --> 00:05:56,350
Yes.

73
00:05:56,440 --> 00:05:57,510
Liu Hanyun killed many bandits

74
00:05:57,510 --> 00:05:59,320
on his way.

75
00:06:00,670 --> 00:06:02,040
Including bandits of Laozi Ridge?

76
00:06:02,830 --> 00:06:03,390
What?

77
00:06:04,600 --> 00:06:06,000
Nothing. I know.

78
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:07,040
You can go back.

79
00:06:28,440 --> 00:06:29,040
Gu Dali!

80
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:30,040
Cao Guixiu!

81
00:06:33,440 --> 00:06:34,270
How did you come in?

82
00:06:34,270 --> 00:06:35,720
It’s none of your business.

83
00:06:35,950 --> 00:06:38,000
What happened? Why were you hurt?

84
00:06:38,270 --> 00:06:38,880
Stop pretending!

85
00:06:39,320 --> 00:06:40,600
I just knocked out your teeth.

86
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:42,270
But you killed my people!

87
00:06:45,350 --> 00:06:46,760
Did something really happen in Laozi Ridge?

88
00:06:48,880 --> 00:07:03,110
♫ I can’t put up with the torture of my step-mother ♫

89
00:07:03,200 --> 00:07:19,230
♫ So I just pick up reed catkins at the wilderness ♫

90
00:07:19,550 --> 00:07:22,510
♫ At home ♫

91
00:07:22,510 --> 00:07:23,390
Stop.

92
00:07:28,230 --> 00:07:30,270
Repeat the sentence that you just sang.

93
00:07:32,880 --> 00:07:41,270
♫ So I just pick up ♫

94
00:07:44,110 --> 00:07:46,200
Why do I feel it

95
00:07:47,350 --> 00:07:48,510
annoying?

96
00:07:52,159 --> 00:07:52,760
Master!

97
00:07:54,230 --> 00:07:54,950
Master!

98
00:07:54,950 --> 00:07:56,640
Our big customer comes. Come.

99
00:07:58,600 --> 00:07:59,670
Keep practicing.

100
00:08:05,510 --> 00:08:07,760
Don’t waste much time at here.

101
00:08:08,110 --> 00:08:10,270
You’ll never step on the stage.

102
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:12,000
Go to the backyard to do the chores.

103
00:08:23,070 --> 00:08:25,600
The goods sent to the commander has arrived.

104
00:08:26,070 --> 00:08:26,640
Fengtai.

105
00:08:28,110 --> 00:08:28,720
Mr. Ma.

106
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:29,270
You are here.

107
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:30,950
Go back.

108
00:08:31,390 --> 00:08:32,110
Yes.

109
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:36,710
How is it going?

110
00:08:38,520 --> 00:08:40,280
Sixi’er has been

111
00:08:40,280 --> 00:08:41,549
in this industry for many years.

112
00:08:41,549 --> 00:08:43,320
He’s too cunning.

113
00:08:44,670 --> 00:08:45,790
I tell you.

114
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:49,030
I ask my man to choose performers in Yunxi.

115
00:08:49,320 --> 00:08:50,550
Do you know what Sixi’er did?

116
00:08:50,760 --> 00:08:52,760
He didn’t show the good ones.

117
00:08:53,320 --> 00:08:54,640
He only asked those

118
00:08:54,640 --> 00:08:56,030
bad performers out.

119
00:08:59,520 --> 00:09:00,200
My men

120
00:09:00,520 --> 00:09:01,400
was afraid to give himself away,

121
00:09:01,400 --> 00:09:03,080
so he didn’t ask about Zhouzi directly.

122
00:09:03,880 --> 00:09:04,400
Also,

123
00:09:05,350 --> 00:09:06,320
Sixi’er said

124
00:09:06,550 --> 00:09:08,200
that he’s an opera master

125
00:09:08,200 --> 00:09:09,320
instead of a trafficker.

126
00:09:09,520 --> 00:09:10,520
And in his words,

127
00:09:11,150 --> 00:09:12,110
these kids are performers.

128
00:09:12,110 --> 00:09:13,910
The time that they work for him can be discussed.

129
00:09:14,350 --> 00:09:15,760
But there’s no way

130
00:09:16,440 --> 00:09:17,550
that they sign the contract.

131
00:09:18,110 --> 00:09:19,520
If we want to

132
00:09:19,520 --> 00:09:20,640
save Zhouzi out,

133
00:09:21,910 --> 00:09:24,400
we need to send a totally strange one

134
00:09:24,640 --> 00:09:26,670
in this circle.

135
00:09:27,520 --> 00:09:28,910
If Sixi’er knows that

136
00:09:28,910 --> 00:09:30,880
Mr. Shang wants Zhouzi,

137
00:09:31,640 --> 00:09:33,030
he will hit Zhouzi to death.

138
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:35,760
Well...

139
00:09:37,230 --> 00:09:38,550
Except the troupes,

140
00:09:38,640 --> 00:09:41,200
who else have opera performers?

141
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:43,280
Only those who are

142
00:09:43,640 --> 00:09:45,910
wealthy and powerful have that time.

143
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:47,280
Where should I find one?

144
00:09:52,200 --> 00:09:52,910
Fengtai.

145
00:09:53,710 --> 00:09:56,320
How about going to the chamber of commerce

146
00:09:56,960 --> 00:09:58,000
and ask for their help?

147
00:09:59,760 --> 00:10:01,320
The chamber belongs to Peking.

148
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:03,440
We can’t even tell a lie.

149
00:10:03,790 --> 00:10:05,440
They’ll easily know it’s me.

150
00:10:07,110 --> 00:10:08,550
Then what’s our next move?

151
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:15,000
Mr. Cheng, Mr. Cao and a guest come to you.

152
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:25,200
He killed many of my people. You won’t avenge?

153
00:10:25,550 --> 00:10:26,150
You can’t!

154
00:10:26,840 --> 00:10:29,000
I’ll revenge for you sooner or later.

155
00:10:29,230 --> 00:10:31,400
I will gain the justice back for your men.

156
00:10:31,880 --> 00:10:34,320
Taking caring yourself is the most important thing.

157
00:10:34,840 --> 00:10:36,150
Come on. Sit down.

158
00:10:40,320 --> 00:10:41,030
Uncle.

159
00:10:42,670 --> 00:10:44,350
Find her a place.

160
00:10:46,910 --> 00:10:49,440
Why don’t you take her

161
00:10:49,440 --> 00:10:50,710
to the barrack?

162
00:10:51,030 --> 00:10:52,000
Look at her.

163
00:10:52,910 --> 00:10:54,000
She can disguise like a man

164
00:10:54,280 --> 00:10:56,200
if she puts on your uniform.

165
00:10:58,350 --> 00:10:59,320
I can’t.

166
00:11:01,760 --> 00:11:03,350
It would be OK four months ago.

167
00:11:04,280 --> 00:11:05,470
But I can’t make it now.

168
00:11:27,440 --> 00:11:28,520
You are so accurate.

169
00:11:29,590 --> 00:11:30,320
Fine.

170
00:11:31,320 --> 00:11:33,710
Seems that I need to congratulate Commander Cao

171
00:11:34,150 --> 00:11:36,320
to have a grandson.

172
00:11:36,790 --> 00:11:39,550
It’s none of that Cao’s business. This is my son.

173
00:11:39,550 --> 00:11:41,230
He’s the successor of Laozi Ridge.

174
00:11:41,230 --> 00:11:42,760
He’ll be the king of bushranger.

175
00:11:50,670 --> 00:11:51,670
What are you laughing for?

176
00:11:52,760 --> 00:11:53,880
You look down on me?

177
00:11:54,230 --> 00:11:56,670
What if it’s a daughter?

178
00:11:56,670 --> 00:11:59,080
She’ll be the queen of bushranger.

179
00:12:03,760 --> 00:12:04,470
Yes.

180
00:12:05,840 --> 00:12:06,350
Well...

181
00:12:07,760 --> 00:12:09,110
The king or the queen

182
00:12:09,590 --> 00:12:10,760
of bushranger,

183
00:12:11,280 --> 00:12:14,230
I think each one is OK.

184
00:12:14,350 --> 00:12:17,200
We should calm down and not take action.

185
00:12:17,840 --> 00:12:19,280
Well, I arrange you a place

186
00:12:19,280 --> 00:12:20,710
in Peking.

187
00:12:21,840 --> 00:12:24,350
Once there’s information of Liu Hanyun,

188
00:12:24,470 --> 00:12:26,080
I’ll tell you immediately.

189
00:12:26,960 --> 00:12:28,960
Thanks, uncle.

190
00:12:29,350 --> 00:12:30,590
No worries.

191
00:12:34,880 --> 00:12:37,960
Liu Hanyun comes to Peking under orders.

192
00:12:38,030 --> 00:12:40,230
Apparently he’s here to inspect economy and security,

193
00:12:40,350 --> 00:12:43,110
but in fact, he comes for the firearms smuggling

194
00:12:43,110 --> 00:12:44,520
of Cao and Cheng.

195
00:12:45,840 --> 00:12:48,590
Uncle, are the firearms that you

196
00:12:48,910 --> 00:12:50,440
gave Laozoi Ridge marked?

197
00:12:51,280 --> 00:12:53,080
I’ve been doing this business for many years.

198
00:12:53,910 --> 00:12:55,960
I won’t leave any mark on the package.

199
00:12:56,640 --> 00:12:59,350
He won’t get any clue through the package.

200
00:13:00,320 --> 00:13:01,150
That’s fine.

201
00:13:02,400 --> 00:13:05,350
I wonder whether he’ll target you obviously

202
00:13:05,960 --> 00:13:07,960
and frame you stealthily.

203
00:13:08,350 --> 00:13:09,960
It’s a Greek gift anyway.

204
00:13:11,000 --> 00:13:12,760
I need to tell the commander now.

205
00:13:14,710 --> 00:13:15,640
By the way, Mr. Cao.

206
00:13:16,230 --> 00:13:17,350
Here’s another thing.

207
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:21,110
Could you do me a favor?

208
00:13:32,320 --> 00:13:34,030
Mrs. Wang. Where are you from?

209
00:13:41,670 --> 00:13:42,960
I am from Shangtung.

210
00:13:46,030 --> 00:13:47,110
Shangtung?

211
00:13:48,320 --> 00:13:50,200
Your dress looks elegant.

212
00:13:50,350 --> 00:13:52,150
Mr. Wang must do some important business.

213
00:13:53,000 --> 00:13:54,440
You are right.

214
00:13:55,960 --> 00:13:58,110
It’s about people’s life.

215
00:14:01,880 --> 00:14:03,590
But he’s busy.

216
00:14:04,550 --> 00:14:07,110
I just want someone who can sing

217
00:14:07,350 --> 00:14:08,640
to kill my time.

218
00:14:19,000 --> 00:14:20,710
This is a right place.

219
00:14:20,710 --> 00:14:21,590
Look.

220
00:14:21,590 --> 00:14:23,350
The best kids are

221
00:14:23,350 --> 00:14:24,470
all here.

222
00:14:24,470 --> 00:14:25,470
They know all

223
00:14:25,470 --> 00:14:26,910
the good places in Peking.

224
00:14:27,000 --> 00:14:28,910
I’m sure they’ll make you brighter.

225
00:14:30,200 --> 00:14:33,350
Mr. Xi, are you fooling me?

226
00:14:35,110 --> 00:14:36,440
Look at them.

227
00:14:36,590 --> 00:14:38,320
No one looks good.

228
00:14:38,440 --> 00:14:39,910
I don’t even want to look at them.

229
00:14:40,000 --> 00:14:41,400
How come they play with me?

230
00:14:42,000 --> 00:14:43,440
What if my baby looks like them

231
00:14:43,440 --> 00:14:44,790
when I always see them?

232
00:14:44,790 --> 00:14:45,760
Will you take the responsibility?

233
00:14:47,910 --> 00:14:48,880
Stop joking.

234
00:14:49,550 --> 00:14:50,280
Mrs. Wang.

235
00:14:50,550 --> 00:14:52,110
What’s your idea?

236
00:14:53,280 --> 00:14:54,710
To be honest,

237
00:14:54,910 --> 00:14:56,520
at Huibin Theater,

238
00:14:56,520 --> 00:14:58,350
I saw a handyman

239
00:14:59,520 --> 00:14:59,910
named...

240
00:15:00,400 --> 00:15:01,640
Zhouzi.

241
00:15:02,840 --> 00:15:04,670
Ask him out.

242
00:15:06,640 --> 00:15:09,110
He’s a coward.

243
00:15:09,110 --> 00:15:10,470
He knows nothing.

244
00:15:10,470 --> 00:15:12,230
I’m afraid he’ll make you angry.

245
00:15:13,520 --> 00:15:15,710
I am the decider.

246
00:15:15,790 --> 00:15:17,400
Ask him out now.

247
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:29,350
If Mrs. Wang likes him,

248
00:15:31,320 --> 00:15:32,790
you’ll be rewarded more handsomely.

249
00:15:35,200 --> 00:15:36,710
OK, Mrs. Wang.

250
00:15:36,710 --> 00:15:37,960
Let me show you the way.

251
00:15:38,200 --> 00:15:39,200
Please. Mrs. Wang.

252
00:15:49,470 --> 00:15:50,320
Leader.

253
00:15:52,670 --> 00:15:55,000
Mrs. Wang. What do you think?

254
00:15:58,320 --> 00:15:59,960
Fine. Prepare your things.

255
00:15:59,960 --> 00:16:01,150
Go with me within this month.

256
00:16:06,350 --> 00:16:08,520
Leader. Where do you want me to go?

257
00:16:09,760 --> 00:16:11,640
Leader, please make me stay.

258
00:16:11,960 --> 00:16:13,350
I serve you and wash your clothes.

259
00:16:13,790 --> 00:16:15,030
At least, I’ll have a chance to

260
00:16:16,030 --> 00:16:17,230
perform on the stage.

261
00:16:18,590 --> 00:16:20,520
Perform on the stage?

262
00:16:21,030 --> 00:16:23,110
Dream on. Jerk.

263
00:16:24,520 --> 00:16:25,150
Alright.

264
00:16:26,790 --> 00:16:28,470
Tie him.

265
00:16:28,880 --> 00:16:30,350
I don’t go! I don’t go!

266
00:16:30,350 --> 00:16:31,080
Let go of me!

267
00:16:31,790 --> 00:16:32,080
Let...

268
00:16:41,000 --> 00:16:42,910
Is this Mrs. Wang a bandit?

269
00:16:52,640 --> 00:16:56,230
Everything is

270
00:16:58,150 --> 00:16:59,640
deiced by his fate.

271
00:17:05,470 --> 00:17:06,310
Get out.

272
00:17:16,500 --> 00:17:18,700
(Peking Opera Association First Theater)

273
00:17:19,700 --> 00:17:33,060
♫ My father Jiang Shao does business outside ♫

274
00:17:52,140 --> 00:18:09,900
♫ I can’t put up with the torture of my step-mother ♫

275
00:18:11,220 --> 00:18:27,620
♫ So I just pick up reed catkins at the wilderness ♫

276
00:18:40,230 --> 00:18:41,430
How old are you?

277
00:18:42,350 --> 00:18:44,590
14.

278
00:18:46,230 --> 00:18:48,920
You are quite outstanding among your peers.

279
00:18:49,760 --> 00:18:50,760
Staying with me,

280
00:18:50,760 --> 00:18:52,470
I can make you better.

281
00:18:52,470 --> 00:18:53,560
Will you?

282
00:18:54,640 --> 00:18:55,350
I...

283
00:18:57,560 --> 00:18:58,640
What’s the matter?

284
00:19:02,000 --> 00:19:02,710
Kid.

285
00:19:15,230 --> 00:19:17,000
Slowly. Don’t be choked.

286
00:19:17,230 --> 00:19:19,000
I don’t know how he sings,

287
00:19:19,310 --> 00:19:21,110
but he looks like you when eating.

288
00:19:22,230 --> 00:19:23,680
Ignore him. Go ahead.

289
00:19:26,880 --> 00:19:28,760
How long haven’t you eaten?

290
00:19:28,760 --> 00:19:29,950
How come you were hungry to faint?

291
00:19:31,160 --> 00:19:31,880
Delicious.

292
00:19:32,590 --> 00:19:34,350
I haven’t eaten meat for years.

293
00:19:35,470 --> 00:19:36,920
He didn’t give you meat?

294
00:19:37,230 --> 00:19:38,920
Did Sixi’er want you to live?

295
00:19:39,110 --> 00:19:41,950
Our leader said that meat ruins our figure.

296
00:19:41,950 --> 00:19:43,430
The audiences don’t like it.

297
00:19:43,430 --> 00:19:44,400
Nonsense.

298
00:19:44,590 --> 00:19:46,560
Mr. Cai is fat enough,

299
00:19:46,560 --> 00:19:47,590
but he’s still popular.

300
00:19:47,590 --> 00:19:48,680
Stop it.

301
00:19:48,920 --> 00:19:50,400
He’s not fat, but plump.

302
00:19:50,760 --> 00:19:53,110
You’ll offend him

303
00:19:53,230 --> 00:19:54,190
if he knows.

304
00:19:56,760 --> 00:19:58,190
Don’t be afraid.

305
00:19:58,560 --> 00:19:59,560
I tell you.

306
00:19:59,560 --> 00:20:00,760
Sixi’er

307
00:20:01,070 --> 00:20:02,560
is not young.

308
00:20:02,560 --> 00:20:05,310
He’s on the way to the tomb.

309
00:20:05,400 --> 00:20:07,070
Just work hard on the opera.

310
00:20:07,070 --> 00:20:09,230
When he’s dead, you’ll be a star.

311
00:20:10,110 --> 00:20:11,070
Mr. Shang.

312
00:20:11,830 --> 00:20:13,760
How can you teach kids this way?

313
00:20:14,680 --> 00:20:16,830
Even though Sixi’er lived to 70,

314
00:20:17,310 --> 00:20:18,880
it’s still 20 years ahead.

315
00:20:19,400 --> 00:20:21,070
What will you do during these years?

316
00:20:22,230 --> 00:20:23,470
Torture him?

317
00:20:24,110 --> 00:20:25,680
He won’t be a star anyway.

318
00:20:25,760 --> 00:20:26,950
Save your lecture.

319
00:20:27,680 --> 00:20:28,830
I put a lot of efforts

320
00:20:28,830 --> 00:20:30,560
into saving Zhouzi from Yunxi.

321
00:20:30,560 --> 00:20:31,470
Why?

322
00:20:31,590 --> 00:20:34,470
Maybe after he steps on the stage, he’ll be popular.

323
00:20:34,920 --> 00:20:35,760
In this industry,

324
00:20:36,430 --> 00:20:37,760
once you are a star,

325
00:20:38,000 --> 00:20:39,470
nothing can be your barrier.

326
00:20:44,760 --> 00:20:46,430
What’s your stage name

327
00:20:46,430 --> 00:20:49,710
when you perform?

328
00:20:50,640 --> 00:20:52,310
You can’t just be named Zhouzi.

329
00:20:53,880 --> 00:20:55,470
I need to think about it.

330
00:20:55,470 --> 00:20:58,000
Please stop it.

331
00:20:58,470 --> 00:21:01,000
Look the names you gave them.

332
00:21:01,310 --> 00:21:03,680
From Zhengyue Hong to Layue Hong.

333
00:21:03,880 --> 00:21:04,950
You never put efforts.

334
00:21:05,110 --> 00:21:06,680
I wasn’t serious on that.

335
00:21:06,680 --> 00:21:07,830
I’ll give him a name seriously.

336
00:21:07,830 --> 00:21:09,760
With my lucky name, he will be a star.

337
00:21:09,880 --> 00:21:11,230
Come on, be serious.

338
00:21:13,400 --> 00:21:14,880
The performers

339
00:21:15,110 --> 00:21:17,400
should have exquisite names,

340
00:21:18,070 --> 00:21:19,680
especially for those who play female roles.

341
00:21:20,760 --> 00:21:21,920
It’s...

342
00:21:26,880 --> 00:21:28,220
How about Zhou Xiangyun?

343
00:21:28,220 --> 00:21:28,230
(Zhou Xiangyun)
How about Zhou Xiangyun?

344
00:21:28,230 --> 00:21:32,340
(Zhou Xiangyun)

345
00:21:35,950 --> 00:21:36,880
Are these words?

346
00:21:36,880 --> 00:21:37,800
Let me have a look.

347
00:21:40,880 --> 00:21:42,800
It sounds delicate.

348
00:21:44,000 --> 00:21:45,880
It also looks good.

349
00:21:47,520 --> 00:21:48,520
See clearly.

350
00:21:48,520 --> 00:21:50,520
It’s awkward if you can’t read your own name.

351
00:22:06,590 --> 00:22:07,190
Mr. Shang.

352
00:22:08,040 --> 00:22:09,110
You are so kind to me.

353
00:22:09,470 --> 00:22:11,430
How can I repay you?

354
00:22:14,040 --> 00:22:15,430
You ate my pork joint.

355
00:22:16,160 --> 00:22:17,310
What will I eat?

356
00:22:17,710 --> 00:22:19,190
When I teach you opera next time,

357
00:22:19,400 --> 00:22:20,470
bring me a new one.

358
00:22:24,110 --> 00:22:24,800
OK, Xiao Lai.

359
00:22:25,400 --> 00:22:27,400
Take him to Shuiyun Theater.

360
00:22:27,470 --> 00:22:29,110
OK, don’t worry.

361
00:22:29,880 --> 00:22:31,000
Stand up.

362
00:22:34,160 --> 00:22:34,950
Go.

363
00:22:38,400 --> 00:22:39,710
He’s just a handyman.

364
00:22:39,920 --> 00:22:42,190
Does he have money to buy pork joint?

365
00:22:43,520 --> 00:22:45,280
Xiao Lai will give him money.

366
00:22:49,400 --> 00:22:50,310
Mr. Shang.

367
00:22:50,680 --> 00:22:52,710
Do you really think he can be a star?

368
00:22:55,760 --> 00:22:58,710
Not all performers can be stars.

369
00:22:59,880 --> 00:23:01,070
What else should he do?

370
00:23:05,160 --> 00:23:08,830
The secret can’t be spoken.

371
00:23:08,830 --> 00:23:10,710
He must feel it by himself.

372
00:23:19,310 --> 00:23:20,800
Your massage is very good.

373
00:23:20,800 --> 00:23:21,680
Of course.

374
00:23:23,430 --> 00:23:23,950
Here.

375
00:23:23,950 --> 00:23:24,680
Give me more.

376
00:23:29,400 --> 00:23:31,280
Is this Sixi’er’s apprentice?

377
00:23:32,110 --> 00:23:33,560
Sixi’er’s apprentice

378
00:23:33,880 --> 00:23:35,830
comes here alone.

379
00:23:36,040 --> 00:23:38,280
What? Will you bring us trouble?

380
00:23:43,560 --> 00:23:44,760
What were you talking about?

381
00:23:47,800 --> 00:23:49,110
Xiao Lai. Please give me.

382
00:23:52,280 --> 00:23:53,520
I tell you.

383
00:23:53,710 --> 00:23:55,110
This is Zhou Xiangyun.

384
00:23:55,560 --> 00:23:57,310
Our leader invited him here.

385
00:23:57,590 --> 00:23:58,920
From now on,

386
00:23:58,920 --> 00:24:00,680
he’ll live here.

387
00:24:00,880 --> 00:24:02,430
He’s an honest guy.

388
00:24:02,880 --> 00:24:05,070
Don’t bully him.

389
00:24:05,310 --> 00:24:06,800
Our leader invited him?

390
00:24:07,430 --> 00:24:10,160
Xiao Lai. Don’t cheat us.

391
00:24:10,560 --> 00:24:12,880
There’s no honest guy in Yunxi.

392
00:24:13,920 --> 00:24:16,230
How come I waste time to cheat you?

393
00:24:16,430 --> 00:24:17,470
When our leader comes back,

394
00:24:17,470 --> 00:24:18,590
you can ask him.

395
00:24:22,430 --> 00:24:24,230
Move your pigsty

396
00:24:24,230 --> 00:24:25,110
for him.

397
00:24:26,430 --> 00:24:27,430
Is this a pigsty?

398
00:24:27,430 --> 00:24:29,070
Don’t bother.

399
00:24:29,640 --> 00:24:32,640
I slept on the chair in Yunxi.

400
00:24:33,800 --> 00:24:35,760
I’m satisfied enough to

401
00:24:36,000 --> 00:24:37,230
have a shelter.

402
00:24:38,110 --> 00:24:39,400
You slept on the chair?

403
00:24:39,920 --> 00:24:41,110
Did you practice the skill of Iron Slab?

404
00:24:41,400 --> 00:24:42,190
Yunxi is harsher

405
00:24:42,190 --> 00:24:43,920
than Shuiyun.

406
00:24:43,920 --> 00:24:45,190
Do you think so, Dasheng?

407
00:24:46,000 --> 00:24:47,040
What are you talking about?

408
00:24:50,350 --> 00:24:52,400
Since the leader let me take care of you,

409
00:24:53,470 --> 00:24:55,430
I need to arrange things well.

410
00:24:58,110 --> 00:24:59,400
You don’t move?

411
00:24:59,590 --> 00:25:01,470
OK, let me do it.

412
00:25:01,470 --> 00:25:02,640
I’ll throw them out.

413
00:25:03,470 --> 00:25:05,190
Xiao Lai. Xiao Lai. Xiao Lai.

414
00:25:05,190 --> 00:25:05,880
I move. I move.

415
00:25:05,880 --> 00:25:06,800
We do it ourselves.

416
00:25:06,800 --> 00:25:08,000
We do it ourselves.

417
00:25:08,470 --> 00:25:08,880
We move.

418
00:25:08,880 --> 00:25:09,520
Hurry. Hurry.

419
00:25:09,520 --> 00:25:09,920
Move.

420
00:25:11,310 --> 00:25:11,880
Quilt.

421
00:25:21,470 --> 00:25:22,680
Hurry up.

422
00:25:28,190 --> 00:25:30,280
OK. It’s late.

423
00:25:30,280 --> 00:25:31,230
Have a rest.

424
00:25:31,350 --> 00:25:32,920
You still need to practice tomorrow.

425
00:25:33,820 --> 00:25:34,750
Xiao Lai. Bye.

426
00:25:34,820 --> 00:25:36,040
-Bye.
-Xiao Lai.

427
00:25:37,000 --> 00:25:39,000
Have a good rest at here.

428
00:25:39,000 --> 00:25:41,310
Don’t think about others.

429
00:25:44,520 --> 00:25:45,640
Xiao Lai. See you.

430
00:25:56,280 --> 00:25:57,190
What?

431
00:25:58,680 --> 00:26:00,160
What are you doing?

432
00:26:00,280 --> 00:26:03,350
Sleep at the corner.

433
00:26:03,920 --> 00:26:06,920
Don’t make us infected with the disease of Sixi’er.

434
00:26:09,160 --> 00:26:10,350
Hurry.

435
00:26:12,000 --> 00:26:13,230
Didn’t you hear?

436
00:26:14,760 --> 00:26:16,000
Don’t touch. It’s dirty.

437
00:26:18,920 --> 00:26:20,000
I’ll sleep.

438
00:26:21,000 --> 00:26:21,590
Dasheng.

439
00:26:35,310 --> 00:26:36,680
What does he mean?

440
00:26:52,070 --> 00:26:52,830
Sleep.

441
00:27:21,230 --> 00:27:21,760
Get lost!

442
00:27:22,400 --> 00:27:23,110
Get out!

443
00:27:36,560 --> 00:27:37,590
What’s happening here?

444
00:27:51,760 --> 00:27:52,920
Did you hurt?

445
00:27:54,230 --> 00:27:54,950
No.

446
00:27:57,830 --> 00:27:59,310
Who did it?

447
00:28:00,640 --> 00:28:02,830
It’s too dark to see clearly.

448
00:28:06,760 --> 00:28:09,760
Don’t be afraid. Tell me.

449
00:28:10,350 --> 00:28:12,000
Don’t be a coward!

450
00:28:15,430 --> 00:28:16,800
Are you sure that you didn’t see it clearly?

451
00:28:25,350 --> 00:28:26,640
Don’t pretend!

452
00:28:28,040 --> 00:28:30,000
You were all triumphant when bullying him.

453
00:28:31,110 --> 00:28:32,800
Stand out to be responsible for what you did.

454
00:28:43,000 --> 00:28:44,710
Dasheng. Are you deaf?

455
00:28:45,350 --> 00:28:47,110
Leader. I was asleep.

456
00:28:47,110 --> 00:28:48,000
Bring my shoes.

457
00:28:50,560 --> 00:28:51,680
Where are the shoes?

458
00:28:53,400 --> 00:28:54,560
I was sleeping.

459
00:28:55,760 --> 00:28:57,680
Leader. The floor is cold. Put them on.

460
00:29:04,640 --> 00:29:06,430
I didn’t blame you for days.

461
00:29:07,190 --> 00:29:08,560
Give an inch and you'll run a mile?

462
00:29:09,040 --> 00:29:11,070
Leader. I swear I don’t know.

463
00:29:11,430 --> 00:29:12,920
I just woke up.

464
00:29:12,920 --> 00:29:16,160
Yes. I was in my dream.

465
00:29:16,520 --> 00:29:18,190
But I was woken up suddenly.

466
00:29:18,760 --> 00:29:19,880
Yes, leader.

467
00:29:19,880 --> 00:29:22,070
Maybe he went out when he was sleepwalking.

468
00:29:22,070 --> 00:29:22,640
Stop!

469
00:29:24,000 --> 00:29:25,760
You are all good at wording.

470
00:29:27,000 --> 00:29:29,590
Why don’t you sing opera with this skill?

471
00:29:31,710 --> 00:29:34,710
Leader. He’s a stranger here.

472
00:29:34,710 --> 00:29:36,160
He’s also a member of Yunxi.

473
00:29:36,430 --> 00:29:39,110
Why did you blame us for him?

474
00:29:39,110 --> 00:29:40,400
Right.

475
00:29:40,640 --> 00:29:43,070
Zhou Xiangyun. Come in!

476
00:29:47,280 --> 00:29:47,920
Come in!

477
00:29:59,350 --> 00:30:01,040
Indeed, he’s a stranger.

478
00:30:01,590 --> 00:30:06,160
But he performs better than all of you.

479
00:30:06,560 --> 00:30:09,430
Leader, I’ll talk back if you say so.

480
00:30:10,230 --> 00:30:12,680
I came from a troupe.

481
00:30:13,000 --> 00:30:14,560
And I’ve been learning opera from you for years.

482
00:30:14,560 --> 00:30:16,470
How come I’m worse than this lad?

483
00:30:16,760 --> 00:30:17,680
Right.

484
00:30:17,680 --> 00:30:18,710
How about this?

485
00:30:19,760 --> 00:30:22,560
I’ll choose an opera.

486
00:30:22,640 --> 00:30:25,920
You select a boy among you to

487
00:30:25,920 --> 00:30:28,000
compete against Zhou Xiangyun.

488
00:30:28,000 --> 00:30:28,880
Do you dare?

489
00:30:28,880 --> 00:30:29,520
Yes.

490
00:30:29,680 --> 00:30:30,680
This lad?

491
00:30:30,680 --> 00:30:31,590
What’s the reward?

492
00:30:31,590 --> 00:30:32,590
If you win, I’ll double your payment

493
00:30:32,590 --> 00:30:34,280
every month.

494
00:30:34,800 --> 00:30:35,590
Really?

495
00:30:36,000 --> 00:30:37,110
Go back to sleep.

496
00:30:39,190 --> 00:30:40,430
Mr. Shang, don’t...

497
00:30:40,430 --> 00:30:41,830
Are you timid?

498
00:30:41,830 --> 00:30:43,520
How can you be a star in the future?

499
00:30:44,640 --> 00:30:47,280
OK, it’s deal.

500
00:30:47,520 --> 00:30:48,310
It’s deal.

501
00:30:48,430 --> 00:30:50,000
You go back with me.

502
00:30:51,640 --> 00:30:53,230
Don’t be frightened tomorrow.

503
00:30:53,920 --> 00:30:55,110
Cut him down to size tomorrow.

504
00:30:55,800 --> 00:30:56,880
What a mess.

505
00:30:58,350 --> 00:30:59,470
Turn off the light. Sleep.

506
00:31:20,160 --> 00:31:22,110
Well... Mr. Shang.

507
00:31:22,800 --> 00:31:23,310
What?

508
00:31:24,400 --> 00:31:25,470
Is the quilt cold?

509
00:31:29,470 --> 00:31:30,230
No.

510
00:31:31,310 --> 00:31:33,000
I...

511
00:31:41,680 --> 00:31:43,000
Listen.

512
00:31:44,760 --> 00:31:46,400
When I was at your age,

513
00:31:47,280 --> 00:31:48,430
I violently beat the one

514
00:31:48,430 --> 00:31:50,430
who drove me out

515
00:31:51,520 --> 00:31:53,190
of the room.

516
00:31:54,230 --> 00:31:56,160
He would be afraid when he saw the bed.

517
00:31:58,190 --> 00:31:59,400
Your courage

518
00:31:59,830 --> 00:32:02,710
has been almost ruined by Sixi’er.

519
00:32:05,070 --> 00:32:07,760
Yes. I’m not confident

520
00:32:08,110 --> 00:32:09,830
in tomorrow’s competition.

521
00:32:12,400 --> 00:32:13,710
Don’t grow apprehensive.

522
00:32:14,400 --> 00:32:15,470
Even if you lost,

523
00:32:15,760 --> 00:32:17,400
I am still your investor.

524
00:32:17,800 --> 00:32:19,310
Just focus on what you sing.

525
00:32:23,230 --> 00:32:25,950
Mr. Shang. It’s so kind of you.

526
00:32:26,880 --> 00:32:29,000
No one was

527
00:32:29,000 --> 00:32:30,110
so kind to me.

528
00:32:31,070 --> 00:32:32,430
In my next life,

529
00:32:33,070 --> 00:32:34,350
I’ll do everything I can

530
00:32:34,590 --> 00:32:35,760
to repay you.

531
00:32:37,160 --> 00:32:37,920
No.

532
00:32:38,190 --> 00:32:38,950
I’ll repay you in this life.

533
00:32:40,310 --> 00:32:41,230
I will...

534
00:33:08,000 --> 00:33:09,520
Layue. Please help us.

535
00:33:11,950 --> 00:33:13,680
I didn’t engage in what you did last night.

536
00:33:14,430 --> 00:33:15,590
I play male roles.

537
00:33:16,160 --> 00:33:17,800
How can I compete against a female role?

538
00:33:17,800 --> 00:33:19,640
You two can play in one show.

539
00:33:19,950 --> 00:33:21,590
You are the best among us.

540
00:33:22,310 --> 00:33:23,710
We’ll get double payment.

541
00:33:23,710 --> 00:33:24,590
Please.

542
00:33:24,590 --> 00:33:25,160
Yes.

543
00:33:30,400 --> 00:33:31,430
Don’t be

544
00:33:31,830 --> 00:33:34,110
nervous later.

545
00:33:34,470 --> 00:33:36,920
Show all of your ability.

546
00:33:37,880 --> 00:33:40,280
I’ll take you to have good food if you win.

547
00:33:40,710 --> 00:33:42,040
I won’t beat you if you lose.

548
00:33:42,190 --> 00:33:42,710
But...

549
00:33:43,640 --> 00:33:45,680
I didn’t perform in front of so many people.

550
00:33:46,430 --> 00:33:47,950
There are only more than ten people.

551
00:33:48,680 --> 00:33:50,430
You’ll face hundreds of audiences

552
00:33:50,430 --> 00:33:51,950
when you perform in a theater.

553
00:33:53,640 --> 00:33:54,680
OK. Stop talking.

554
00:33:54,680 --> 00:33:56,190
Show yourself.

555
00:33:56,190 --> 00:33:56,830
Go.

556
00:34:09,870 --> 00:34:11,560
Let’s see his ability.

557
00:34:11,560 --> 00:34:12,389
Yes.

558
00:34:16,150 --> 00:34:19,320
I am Layue Hong, a performer who plays old men.

559
00:34:20,000 --> 00:34:23,320
I am Zhouzi... I am Zhou Xiangyun,

560
00:34:23,800 --> 00:34:25,840
a performer who plays females.

561
00:34:27,469 --> 00:34:29,670
He can’t even say his roles clearly.

562
00:34:30,320 --> 00:34:32,120
I’m afraid that he’ll terribly lose.

563
00:34:36,600 --> 00:34:38,670
Sing Meilong Town. Can you?

564
00:34:39,800 --> 00:34:41,389
Zhou Xiangyun. It starts from you.

565
00:34:50,600 --> 00:34:55,120
♫ The moon lights up the whole world ♫

566
00:34:55,320 --> 00:34:59,840
♫ Where are you from ♫

567
00:35:00,600 --> 00:35:02,000
What’s this?

568
00:35:02,230 --> 00:35:03,000
Not good.

569
00:35:05,360 --> 00:35:06,760
What’s wrong with this guy?

570
00:35:07,040 --> 00:35:09,710
Mr. Shang, I’m too nervous.

571
00:35:09,710 --> 00:35:11,190
Please give me one more chance.

572
00:35:11,320 --> 00:35:14,320
Take it easy. Think before you sing.

573
00:35:15,230 --> 00:35:16,840
Calm down.

574
00:35:17,710 --> 00:35:20,230
Good opera comes when you are relaxed,

575
00:35:20,600 --> 00:35:22,800
not when you are laborious.

576
00:35:30,470 --> 00:35:34,630
♫ The moon lights up the whole world ♫

577
00:35:34,630 --> 00:35:39,710
♫ Where are you from ♫

578
00:35:39,710 --> 00:35:42,840
♫ Feng, don’t ask me ♫

579
00:35:42,840 --> 00:35:45,870
♫ Every corner in this world is my home ♫

580
00:35:46,280 --> 00:35:49,560
♫ Sir, please don’t say that ♫

581
00:35:49,560 --> 00:35:53,910
♫ You shouldn’t flirt our good girls ♫

582
00:35:53,910 --> 00:35:57,000
♫ Good girls ♫

583
00:35:57,000 --> 00:35:59,320
♫ Never wear begonia ♫

584
00:35:59,320 --> 00:36:01,150
♫ You are bashful ♫

585
00:36:01,150 --> 00:36:03,950
♫ Which looks very pretty ♫

586
00:36:03,950 --> 00:36:07,800
♫ This begonia makes you dissolute ♫

587
00:36:07,800 --> 00:36:11,040
♫ Begonia begonia ♫

588
00:36:11,040 --> 00:36:13,840
♫ It was taken by ♫

589
00:36:17,280 --> 00:36:17,950
By whom?

590
00:36:18,280 --> 00:36:18,840
What a terrible show.

591
00:36:18,840 --> 00:36:19,950
How to continue?

592
00:36:21,950 --> 00:36:22,600
Zhou Xiangyun.

593
00:36:23,040 --> 00:36:24,190
You were invited by our leader.

594
00:36:24,560 --> 00:36:26,320
I thought you were capable.

595
00:36:26,840 --> 00:36:27,800
Is this all your capacity?

596
00:36:28,910 --> 00:36:30,470
You are even worse than an apprentice.

597
00:36:31,230 --> 00:36:32,800
Layue Hong, what did you say?

598
00:36:33,430 --> 00:36:35,320
He’s just lack of experience.

599
00:36:35,320 --> 00:36:36,520
He’s not like you guys.

600
00:36:36,520 --> 00:36:38,560
Our leader is good enough to you.

601
00:36:38,840 --> 00:36:39,800
Xiao Lai.

602
00:36:40,280 --> 00:36:42,470
You’ve been speaking for him since he came.

603
00:36:42,670 --> 00:36:44,320
Do you have a crush on him

604
00:36:44,320 --> 00:36:46,190
because he looks good?

605
00:36:46,190 --> 00:36:47,520
-What did you say?
-What did you say?

606
00:36:47,520 --> 00:36:48,760
Shut your mouth!

607
00:36:48,760 --> 00:36:50,150
Our leader is still here.

608
00:36:50,320 --> 00:36:51,470
Stop your nonsense!

609
00:36:51,470 --> 00:36:52,670
Stop it.

610
00:36:56,670 --> 00:36:58,560
I heard your voice before.

611
00:36:59,320 --> 00:37:00,950
I know your ability is more than this.

612
00:37:01,670 --> 00:37:04,560
Leader. Don’t find excuse for him.

613
00:37:04,630 --> 00:37:05,600
Please

614
00:37:05,600 --> 00:37:06,910
announce the result.

615
00:37:07,190 --> 00:37:08,560
Please announce it.

616
00:37:08,560 --> 00:37:09,470
We’re waiting for the double payment.

617
00:37:09,470 --> 00:37:10,610
Obviously, we won. Leader.

618
00:37:10,690 --> 00:37:12,240
-Yes.
-Don’t cheat us.

619
00:37:12,360 --> 00:37:14,430
Yes, the result is obvious.

620
00:37:14,430 --> 00:37:15,320
Announce, please.

621
00:37:17,840 --> 00:37:20,000
Mr. Shang. Come to have breakfast with me.

622
00:37:20,470 --> 00:37:22,430
Just one sentence. Wait for a while.

623
00:37:22,430 --> 00:37:23,150
Let’s talk about it when I’m back.

624
00:37:23,520 --> 00:37:23,800
What?

625
00:37:24,080 --> 00:37:25,430
Leader! Leader!

626
00:37:25,430 --> 00:37:26,670
Don’t regret!

627
00:37:27,190 --> 00:37:28,630
Leader. Don’t regret!

628
00:37:30,910 --> 00:37:32,630
Mr. Cheng, you came so early today.

629
00:37:33,320 --> 00:37:35,040
I was standing at the door for a while.

630
00:37:35,760 --> 00:37:37,760
So I didn’t miss this wonderful show.

631
00:37:39,470 --> 00:37:40,670
What a wonderful show?

632
00:37:41,230 --> 00:37:42,320
They didn’t even open their mouth.

633
00:37:42,560 --> 00:37:43,630
It was like meow.

634
00:37:43,630 --> 00:37:44,560
It really made me angry.

635
00:37:45,630 --> 00:37:46,840
So what’s the result you’ll give?

636
00:37:49,120 --> 00:37:50,430
How can you make Zhouzi the winner

637
00:37:51,280 --> 00:37:52,470
after he ruined his performance?

638
00:37:52,470 --> 00:37:54,000
Of course I can’t.

639
00:37:54,430 --> 00:37:55,230
He really made me embarrassed

640
00:37:55,910 --> 00:37:57,040
with his performance.

641
00:37:57,800 --> 00:38:00,950
You heard what Zhouzi sang.

642
00:38:01,560 --> 00:38:04,280
He was too nervous to perform well today.

643
00:38:05,840 --> 00:38:07,600
If he loses this time,

644
00:38:08,560 --> 00:38:11,840
his life will be hard in Shuiyun Theater.

645
00:38:12,000 --> 00:38:12,600
Respect

646
00:38:13,600 --> 00:38:14,910
is gained by themselves.

647
00:38:16,190 --> 00:38:17,150
No one can help them if they don’t work hard.

648
00:38:18,840 --> 00:38:19,950
Those boys only accept

649
00:38:20,950 --> 00:38:21,870
the ones who are capable.

650
00:38:22,670 --> 00:38:24,320
If I am partial to Zhouzi,

651
00:38:24,320 --> 00:38:25,320
they’ll cruelly torture him

652
00:38:25,320 --> 00:38:27,190
in private.

653
00:38:28,320 --> 00:38:29,670
I also experienced this when I was young.

654
00:38:29,840 --> 00:38:30,840
No one protected me.

655
00:38:30,840 --> 00:38:31,840
I gained what I have on my own.

656
00:38:32,520 --> 00:38:34,000
You never had stage freight?

657
00:38:34,320 --> 00:38:35,080
Of course I had.

658
00:38:36,000 --> 00:38:38,600
Any face person will be timid.

659
00:38:40,150 --> 00:38:41,670
How did you overcome it?

660
00:38:42,600 --> 00:38:43,800
When I first stepped on the stage,

661
00:38:44,320 --> 00:38:46,870
it felt like my legs and mouth were not mine.

662
00:38:47,280 --> 00:38:49,800
My father took off my clothes and

663
00:38:50,280 --> 00:38:52,760
asked me to go home from the theater.

664
00:38:54,430 --> 00:38:57,190
I was so ashamed.

665
00:38:57,800 --> 00:38:59,760
Your dad was cruel.

666
00:39:00,760 --> 00:39:03,280
I couldn’t think of such a way even in my next life.

667
00:39:03,320 --> 00:39:04,150
Actually,

668
00:39:04,630 --> 00:39:07,600
after you are totally humiliated,

669
00:39:07,670 --> 00:39:08,950
you won’t be

670
00:39:08,950 --> 00:39:11,080
craven anymore.

671
00:39:14,040 --> 00:39:15,360
Don’t apply this

672
00:39:15,360 --> 00:39:16,670
on Zhouzi.

673
00:39:17,120 --> 00:39:19,360
He didn’t dare to sing in front of more than 10 people.

674
00:39:20,000 --> 00:39:21,840
If you ask him to walk on the street nakedly,

675
00:39:22,230 --> 00:39:24,000
he may suicide tomorrow.

676
00:39:28,280 --> 00:39:29,600
I got it.

677
00:39:30,800 --> 00:39:34,710
You mean Zhouzi has a thin skin

678
00:39:34,710 --> 00:39:36,040
and I have a thick skin?

679
00:39:40,840 --> 00:39:41,630
Change your way.

680
00:39:43,150 --> 00:39:44,710
You are smart.

681
00:39:45,230 --> 00:39:47,630
It’s a piece of cake for you to teach a kid.

682
00:39:48,120 --> 00:39:49,230
Of course.

683
00:39:49,630 --> 00:39:51,040
I’ll make it now.

684
00:39:55,080 --> 00:39:56,360
Are you full?

685
00:39:58,230 --> 00:40:00,760
Leader. Leader. Leader.

686
00:40:01,560 --> 00:40:02,760
Layue Hong won.

687
00:40:02,950 --> 00:40:03,630
From now on,

688
00:40:03,630 --> 00:40:05,280
every one of you will have

689
00:40:05,280 --> 00:40:06,080
double payment.

690
00:40:06,320 --> 00:40:07,560
Nice!

691
00:40:07,670 --> 00:40:08,470
Good news.

692
00:40:09,670 --> 00:40:10,470
Good.

693
00:40:12,000 --> 00:40:13,320
Zhou Xiangyun, follow me.

694
00:40:14,360 --> 00:40:15,630
Mr. Shang, where will we go?

695
00:40:15,630 --> 00:40:16,560
Go! What are you waiting for?

696
00:40:16,560 --> 00:40:17,560
Follow him. Stop talking.

697
00:40:17,560 --> 00:40:18,230
Good.

698
00:40:21,520 --> 00:40:22,320
Mr. Shang.

699
00:40:22,760 --> 00:40:23,670
Have a seat.

700
00:40:24,230 --> 00:40:24,910
Waiter.

701
00:40:24,910 --> 00:40:25,950
Serve Mr. Shang.

702
00:40:26,560 --> 00:40:27,800
Mr. Shang, please have a seat.

703
00:40:28,190 --> 00:40:29,000
Sit.

704
00:40:30,630 --> 00:40:31,560
I tell you.

705
00:40:31,760 --> 00:40:34,150
The meat sauce noodles taste good here.

706
00:40:34,360 --> 00:40:35,280
What else do you want to eat?

707
00:40:35,280 --> 00:40:36,080
Order what you want.

708
00:40:36,710 --> 00:40:38,600
I lost the game and face.

709
00:40:38,870 --> 00:40:40,320
I also made you lose money.

710
00:40:41,710 --> 00:40:42,630
Don’t you blame me?

711
00:40:43,190 --> 00:40:44,320
Will it work?

712
00:40:45,320 --> 00:40:47,000
Won’t you be timid if I blame you?

713
00:40:48,040 --> 00:40:50,870
Don’t be hurried. Step by step.

714
00:40:53,360 --> 00:40:54,800
Mr. Shang. It’s so kind of you.

715
00:40:55,430 --> 00:40:57,150
Stop talking these now. Let’s order.

716
00:40:57,150 --> 00:40:59,040
You are as thin as a monkey.

717
00:41:02,150 --> 00:41:04,360
I only need noodles with nothing.

718
00:41:04,360 --> 00:41:05,470
How come?

719
00:41:06,120 --> 00:41:06,600
Sir.

720
00:41:07,520 --> 00:41:08,840
Tow bowls of meat sauce noodles.

721
00:41:08,840 --> 00:41:11,040
More meat, less noodles and 4 eggs.

722
00:41:11,040 --> 00:41:12,670
Also, 1 kilo sauced beef.

723
00:41:12,840 --> 00:41:16,120
-OK.
-Mr. Shang. Can we finish these?

724
00:41:16,120 --> 00:41:18,120
You’ll finish if you eat a whole day at here.

725
00:41:18,120 --> 00:41:20,560
How can you learn opera if you are not full?

726
00:41:21,320 --> 00:41:23,190
Sir, two bowls of lamp soup.

727
00:41:23,190 --> 00:41:24,320
We need relish.

728
00:41:24,320 --> 00:41:25,670
OK, I’ll give you later.

729
00:41:25,670 --> 00:41:26,670
Here.

730
00:41:26,670 --> 00:41:27,470
Soup.

731
00:41:28,800 --> 00:41:29,600
Here.

732
00:41:30,520 --> 00:41:31,360
Your soup.

733
00:41:33,870 --> 00:41:34,390
Yours.

734
00:41:49,080 --> 00:41:49,840
Your noodles.

735
00:41:55,910 --> 00:41:56,600
Please enjoy.

736
00:42:01,910 --> 00:42:03,320
What are you waiting for? Eat.

737
00:42:05,520 --> 00:42:07,520
Mr. Shang. You are so good.

738
00:42:08,670 --> 00:42:10,190
I’ll work hard to repay you.

739
00:42:11,040 --> 00:42:12,360
I don’t need your repayment.

740
00:42:12,360 --> 00:42:12,950
Eat.

741
00:42:20,320 --> 00:42:21,470
Excuse me? Can I have my bill?

742
00:42:21,710 --> 00:42:22,320
Yes.
